(BETA V5) DoublePulsar Framework
{Changelog}
<General>
- Settings tab is now available - Changelog tab is now available - Embedded GitHub API - Fixed various issues
(Settings Tab)
- Embedded user profiles (Pending Improvements) - Added option to release all IP Configurations
<User Interface>
(Settings Tab)
- Enabled server side profile titles - Enabled server side profile descriptions - Enabled client side custom user avatars - Enabled "Discard all" option for effective data deletion upon request - Added Form opacity adjustment slider - Added monitor brightness adjustment slider
(Changelog Tab)
- Updated the TextBox accordingly
<Coding>
- Github Repository is now open - All further updates will be directly pushed there
